on handler","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"when the redirect completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Due to the nature of iOS, very little concrete information can be gained"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"during this process, as all actions take place in either the Safari app"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"or the sandboxed SFSafariViewController class. The context attempts to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"detect when the user has completed the necessary redirect action by listening","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for both app foregrounds and url callbacks received in the app delegate."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"However, it is possible the when the redirect is “completed”, the user may"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"have not actually completed the necessary actions to authorize the charge.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You should not use either this class, nor "},{"code":"STPAPIClient","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", as a way","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to determine when you should charge the Source or to determine if the redirect","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was successful. Use Stripe webhooks on your backend server to listen for Source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"state changes and to make the charge."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-ios\/documentation\/Stripe\/STPRedirectContext","kind":"symbol","title":"STPRedirectContext","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.stripe.stripe-ios/documentation/Stripe":{"title":"Stripe","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/stripe","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-ios\/documentation\/Stripe","abstract":[]},"doc://com.stripe.stripe-ios/documentation/Stripe/STPRedirectContext/presentationCo